<item>
 <title>Putting you in the driving seat</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/putting-you-driving-seat</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-info field--type-text-long field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;media-vimeo-video media-element file-default media-vimeo-5&quot;&gt;
&lt;iframe class=&quot;media-vimeo-player&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; height=&quot;360&quot; title=&quot;SDS — Putting you in the driving seat&quot; src=&quot;//player.vimeo.com/video/191132306?color=&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot;&gt;Video of SDS — Putting you in the driving seat&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-who field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Who is it for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Putting You In the Driving Seat is intended to raise awareness among people in recovery and practitioners about how SDS can support recovery. &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Putting You In the Driving Seat provides a short, accessible introduction to SDS, gives some examples of how it can be used to support recovery, busts some myths about SDS and explains how to go about accessing it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How can you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Putting You In the Driving Seat can be shown to individuals on laptops, tablets, smart phones and screened to groups using a laptop/projector.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
